{"tid":25243,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施蒙尼：我既未來 係做國際米蘭領隊！！","createTime":"2016-12-06T04:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T04:34:56.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53c05cd3e98db52ff54158df280bd9bdc41b7033","tid":25243,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"馬體會主帥施蒙尼在接受采訪時談到了自己的未來，他表示自己未來會執教國際米蘭。<br />\n施蒙尼和馬體會的合同到2018年到期，這名阿根廷主帥的未來一直和國際米蘭聯繫在一起。此前西蒙尼的兒子基奧雲尼聲稱，自己的父親未來肯定會執教國際米蘭。<br />\n<br />\n對此西蒙尼表示：&ldquo;現在我的未來很明朗，對此我也沒什麼好說的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;關於未來，我和我的家人說了很多，每個人都知道未來我會成為國米的教練，這沒什麼新鮮的。"},{"pid":"9f5fc8294003de91ef15990a28903447cc3ef972","tid":25243,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bd1a958092f7a16ebae845724226fa0ef09c08","tid":25243,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"應該打晒J"},{"pid":"2b60d149d0dad468f5ba434960617c8dee5917e3","tid":25243,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會接埋個仔去國米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca7cbe81fd9a2a19288fd64d2e43b713670affa","tid":25243,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"又係大陸佬d波，依條茅柴同大陸西有咩關係"},{"pid":"a5ef08a848716fad35f4776864a2d237f4ee9d8e","tid":25243,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"國米人腳其實唔差"}]}